entries.femaleVariant: V, wake up!

entries.maleVariant: It's only two, but time's not on our side, River. We splittin' up?

Let's go with Edgewood. Got a strong feelin' about it.
Poppy's the better bet – voice in my gut says so.
OK, let's ride.

Right here. Slot it in, jack into the computer. I wanna see it on the monitor.

No, I... Well, yes... No, no I'm not... Well shit...

Focus or you'll lose it.

Fuck!
Fuck…
Hold on, Randy... Please hold on.
